name: Hand Highlighted Prints of "Nā Pulelehua" on stretched canvas
description:
Limited Edition Hand Highlighted "Nā Pulelehua" Art printed on stretched canvas


Get your very own version of the "Nā Pulelehua" painting by Colleen Wilcox that graces the cover of Anuhea's new album "Butterflies"!

High quality, limited edition giclee (gee-clay) reproductions of the "Na Pulelehua" painting have been printed on stretched canvas. The giclees are gallery wrapped (printing continues around the sides) so they are ready to hang and framing is not necessary. They are printed with archival inks and sealed with a UV resistant coating that protects the image for 75+ years. Colleen Wilcox will hand-highlight each print to make it look almost identical to the original.  They will be signed by both the artist Colleen Wilcox, and Anuhea.

These art pieces are super limited... we're only making 40 of them total, and yours will be numbered by the artist herself.

Each order will also come with a personalized "Butterflies" album signed by Anuhea, stickers, and a personalized autographed poster.


-Allow 4 weeks for production and delivery of the art piece.
-CD, poster and stickers will be delivered as soon as you place your order 
-PRICE INCLUDES SHIPPING AND HANDLING TO THE U.S.!
-Additional shipping costs for international orders.

Holiday Sale Price 15% off

16 x 20 Originally $949  --->  $806.65
24 x 30 Originally $1699 ---> $1444.15




Serious inquiries can direct any questions to anuheajams@gmail.com



*The third picture shows Colleen and Anuhea holding the original painting, which is 24 x 30 inches in size.

An aluminum print is high quality ink infused onto post-consumer recycled aluminum panels for a vibrant, modern, high definition look. Archival coated (lasts for 80+ years) and is scratch resistant. Panels are lightweight, float mounted, and ready to hang.

They are each signed by both the artist Colleen Wilcox, and Anuhea. 

These art pieces are super limited... we're only making 100 of them total, and yours will be numbered by the artist herself.

name: DELUXE Songwriters Delight Package!
description:
For all you aspiring ʻukulele players and songwriters!

This deluxe package includes the beautiful "Nā Pulelehua" Songwriting Notebook signed on the inside cover by Anuhea.

Youʻll also get an 11x17 'Ukulele Chord Chart Poster, designed and signed by Anuhea, which shows you all the chords youʻll need to play almost every song.

You'll also get copies of 2 of Anuheaʻs handwritten lyric sheets, complete with 'ukulele chords, for the songs "Forever Summer" and "Simple Love Song".  

Every deluxe Songwriters Delight Package also comes with Anuhea stickers.

Perfect for a present for yourself, or your aspiring singer!

name: Autographed Songwriting Notebooks
description:
Aspring to be a singer or songwriter someday? Or are you already into it, and need a place to gather your newest inspiration?

These notebooks have 80 pages of lined recycled paper, and feature the beautiful artwork of Colleen Wilcox on the front and back.

Anuhea has signed the inside cover of each notebook, and each order comes with a few Anuhea stickers.

name: 11x17 Autographed "Nā Pulelehua" Butterflies Poster & CD Combo!
description:
Get a deal when you purchase the CD and poster together!

This package contains an 11x17 Autographed "Nā Pulelehua" Butterflies poster and a copy of Anuhea's latest CD "Butterflies"!

The high quality poster is printed on 11x17 card stock paper, and has been signed by both the artist Colleen Wilcox and Anuhea.

Anuhea's new dual disc album "Butterflies" features 2 cds, one full of LIVE recordings over the past few years of touring, and a bonus disc with 3 songs including "Forever Summer", "Perfect Day" and "High On Love". The album packaging is beautiful, and is complete with a lyric book with behind the scenes pictures from touring, and information about each song.

Anuhea will also throw in a couple of stickers with each order.

**Note: the poster and cd are not available for personalization at this time. Just a basic autograph will be made on both the poster and the cd. :)

name: "Anuheake'alaokalokelani" Tank (Women's)
description:
Anuheake'alaokalokelani translates to 'the cool fragrance of the heavenly rose'. It's also Anuhea's full Hawaiian name, given to her by her great grandmother (tutu). The tank is a soft, 98% cotton 2% spandex blend. A pretty light blue color and white print. Design also features the Hawaiian islands among the lettering.

Trip some people out with this Hawaiian tongue twister tank!

This design features an abstract bamboo design in pink with Anuhea's full Hawaiian name below.  The words "Grown on Maui" are on the front, and "An Original Maui Thing" are on the back along with Anuhea's signature.

This is THE first Anuhea shirt ever officially made. Get your hands on one of these gems before they're all history!
